---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---
<section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Core Competencies</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-4xl font-serif">
        Engineering Trust in a Complex World
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-muted-foreground font-sans max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Moving beyond "Check-the-box" compliance to build resilient, security-first organizations that scale.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
      <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Asset First Security -->
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-foreground font-serif">
            <Icon name="mdi:shield-lock-outline" class="h-6 w-6 flex-none text-secondary" />
            <Icon name="mdi:shield-lock-outline" class="h-6 w-6 flex-none text-primary" />
            Asset-First Security
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground font-sans">
            <p class="flex-auto">Focusing on what truly matters: your critical assets. Identifying, classifying, and protecting data where it lives, ensuring your security posture is robust from the inside out.</p>
          </dd>
        </div>
         <!-- GRC Engineering -->
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-foreground font-serif">
            <Icon name="mdi:code-braces" class="h-6 w-6 flex-none text-primary" />
            GRC Engineering
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground font-sans">
            <p class="flex-auto">Treating compliance as code. Automating controls, implementing continuous monitoring, and tightly integrating security requirements into your development lifecycle.</p>
          </dd>
        </div>
         <!-- Strategic Advisory -->
         <div class="flex flex-col">
          <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-foreground font-serif">
            <Icon name="mdi:compass-outline" class="h-6 w-6 flex-none text-primary" />
             Governance Strategy
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground font-sans">
            <p class="flex-auto">Aligning security initiatives with business goals. Creating flexible governance frameworks that enable speed and innovation without compromising trust or safety.</p>
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
